title: 340. Andy & DJ CTI: Ukrainian Super-Soldiers, Climate Emergency & 76 Million Year Old Dinosaur Skeleton
itunes:title: 340. Andy & DJ CTI: Ukrainian Super-Soldiers, Climate Emergency & 76 Million Year Old Dinosaur Skeleton
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss Russian lawmakers blaming losses on experimental Ukrainian super-soldiers, Durbin claiming climate change is more important than the current economic inflation, and a 76 million-year-old dinosaur skeleton being auctioned in New York City.
